00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:20.630 position:56%
It's good to be here at the
Library of Congress, good to see all

00:05:20.630 --> 00:05:25.110
of you beautiful, handsome
young people.

00:05:25.110 --> 00:05:26.410
You look so wonderful.

00:05:26.410 --> 00:05:29.670
You look so smart.

00:05:29.670 --> 00:05:41.850 position:56%
When I go and speak about this book,
reread the book, turn the pages,

00:05:41.850 --> 00:05:46.810
and see certain drawings
