00:06:27.020 --> 00:06:29.520
with some of my brothers
and sisters and cousins.

00:06:29.520 --> 00:06:34.690
We went to a little library
to try to get a library card,

00:06:34.690 --> 00:06:39.100
trying to check out some books,
and we were told by the librarian

00:06:39.100 --> 00:06:41.840
that the library was for
whites only and not for colors.

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:47.520
I didn't go back to that library
