00:30:22.850 --> 00:30:24.510
Where did you get that
strength from?

00:30:24.510 --> 00:30:26.610
What do you want these
young people to know

00:30:26.610 --> 00:30:29.130
about the notion of good trouble?

00:30:29.130 --> 00:30:31.890
Maybe just as impatient, how
do you know you're getting

00:30:31.890 --> 00:30:35.250
