Well, it's very simple.

00:30:37.610 --> 00:30:41.770
When I was growing up and would
visit the little town of Troy,

00:30:41.770 --> 00:30:48.550
visit Montgomery, Troy's about
ten miles from where I grew up.

00:30:48.550 --> 00:30:53.250
You go downtown Troy, you see the
