you have an obligation

00:31:44.390 --> 00:31:47.410
to say something, to do something.

00:31:47.410 --> 00:31:49.500
We cannot afford to be silent.

00:31:49.500 --> 00:31:54.890
Because if we're silent, if you
think you like being mistreated,

00:31:54.890 --> 00:32:03.040
you have to resist, and
say that's not right,

00:32:03.040 --> 00:32:07.160
that's not fair, that's not just.

00:32:08.230 --> 00:32:12.110
