00:39:45.780 --> 00:39:49.370
growing up on that farm,
I wanted to be a minister,

00:39:49.370 --> 00:39:51.750
and we used to raise chickens.

00:39:51.750 --> 00:39:55.240
And with the help of my
brothers and sisters and cousins,

00:39:55.240 --> 00:39:58.200
we would gather all of our chickens
together in the chicken yard,

00:39:58.200 --> 00:40:04.760
