00:40:27.110 --> 00:40:28.410
to me today in the Congress.

00:40:28.410 --> 00:40:31.750
And some of those chickens were
just a little more productive,

00:40:31.750 --> 00:40:33.090
at least they produced eggs,

00:40:33.090 --> 00:40:35.290
